title: Introduction to Machine Learning
description: Covers the classic methods for dimension reduction, supervised classification and cluster analysis. What is special about this unit is the use ot high-dimensional data visualisation to explain emothds, and to diagnose models.

title: Diving Deeper into Data
description: This is an advanced exploratory data analysiis unit, that is based on the spirit of Tukey, to discover the unexpected in data. It has a large focus on making effective plots of data, and checking for suprious structure with modern methods of inference for graphics.
